{
  "name": "ShapeNodes",
  "summary": "<p>每一个 <strong>ShapeNode</strong> 对象都代表任意多边形中线段间的结点或任意多边形曲线段的控点。您可以手动创建或通过使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shapes/Shapes .htm#Shapes.BuildFreeform\">BuildFreeform</a></strong> 和 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FreeformBuilder/FreeformBuilder .htm#FreeformBuilder.ConvertToShape\">ConvertToShape</a></strong> 方法来创建任意多边形。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shape/Shape .htm#Shape.Nodes\">Nodes</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ShapeNodes/ShapeNodes .htm#ShapeNodes.ShapeNodes\">ShapeNodes</a></strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作表上形状三中的结点四。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ShapeNodes/ShapeNodes .htm#ShapeNodes.Insert\">Insert</a></strong> 方法可创建一个新结点并将它添加到 <strong>ShapeNodes</strong> 集合。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表上的形状三中的结点四之后添加一带有曲线段的平滑结点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Insert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>, msoSegmentCurve, msoEditingSmooth, <span class=\"hljs-number\">210</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Nodes</strong>(index)（其中index是结点索引号）可返回一个 <strong>ShapeNode</strong> 对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上形状三中的结点一设置为平滑顶点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetEditingType</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, msoEditingSmooth)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的任意多边形中所有 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ShapeNode/ShapeNode .htm#ShapeNode.ShapeNode\">ShapeNode</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Integer</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第一个形状的节点数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表中第一个形状的第二个节点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作表中第二个形状的最后一个节点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>(nodes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int 精度）",
          "description": "<p>要删除对象的索引。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Insert",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>在任意多边形形状中插入节点。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例选择活动工作表的第三个形状，检查该形状是否是一个任意多边形对象，如果是，则插入一个节点。此示例假定在活动工作表中存在三个形状。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoFreeform) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Insert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, msoSegmentCurve, msoEditingSymmetric, <span class=\"hljs-number\">35</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = msoTrue\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This shape is not a Freeform object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中第二个形状末尾插入新的形状节点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Insert</span>(nodes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, msoSegmentLine, msoEditingAuto, <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int 精度）",
          "description": "<p><strong>Long</strong> 型。形状节点的编号，将在该节点后插入新节点。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "SegmentType",
          "type": "MsoSegmentType",
          "description": "<p>线段类型。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "EditingType",
          "type": "MsoEditingType",
          "description": "<p>编辑的类型。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "X1",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，那么此参数就以磅为单位指定文档的左上角与新线段的终点之间的水平距离。如果新节点的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，那么此参数就以磅为单位指定文档的左上角与新线段的第一个控制点之间的水平距离。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Y1",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档左上角到新线段终点的垂直距离。如果新节点的 <em>EditingType</em> 属性为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档左上角到新线段第一个控制点的垂直距离。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "X2",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 属性为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档左上角到新线段第二个控制点的水平距离。如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，则不用为此参数指定值。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Y2",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档左上角到新线段第二个控制点的垂直距离。如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，则不用为此参数指定值。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "X3",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档的左上角到新线段终点之间的水平距离。如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，则不用为此参数指定值。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Y3",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingCorner</strong>，则此参数就以磅为单位指定从文档左上角到新线段终点的垂直距离。如果新线段的 <em>EditingType</em> 为 <strong>msoEditingAuto</strong>，则不用为此参数指定值。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetEditingType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>设置由 <em>Index</em> 指定的结点的编辑类型。如果该结点是一个曲线的控制点，本方法将对其设置相邻结点的编辑属性，该属性连接两个段。请注意，由于编辑类型的不同，本方法可能影响相邻结点的位置。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第三个形状中的所有结点更改为光滑结点。第三个形状必须是任意多边形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= nodes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetEditingType</span>(i, msoEditingSmooth)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第一个形状的第二个结点更改为对称的曲线结点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetEditingType</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, msoEditingSymmetric)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int 精度）",
          "description": "<p>需要设置编辑类型的顶点。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "EditingType",
          "type": "MsoEditingType",
          "description": "<p>顶点的编辑属性。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetPosition",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>设置由 <em>Index</em> 指定的顶点位置。注意：由于顶点的编辑类型不同，此方法可能影响相邻顶点的位置。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第三个形状中的节点 2 移至距离工作表左侧 200 磅，距离工作表顶部 300 磅。第三个形状必须是任意多边形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetPosition</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中所有形状的节点 1 移至距离工作表左侧 100 磅，距离工作表顶部 200 磅。所有形状必须是任意多边形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= shapes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetPosition</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int 精度）",
          "description": "<p>要设置位置的顶点。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "X1",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>新顶点相对于文档左上角的位置（以磅为单位）。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Y1",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>新顶点相对于文档左上角的位置（以磅为单位）。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetSegmentType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>设置 <em>Index</em> 指定的结点后面的段的段类型。如果该结点为一条曲线段的控制点，则该方法设置该曲线的段��型。请注意，该方法可能由于插入或删除相邻的结点而影响结点总数。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第三个形状的所有线段更改为曲线段。 第三个形状必须是任意多边形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= nodes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetSegmentType</span>(i, msoSegmentCurve)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第二个形状的第二个节点的线段类型设置为直线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nodes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Nodes</span>\n    nodes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetSegmentType</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, msoSegmentLine)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int 精度）",
          "description": "<p>要设置段类型的顶点。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
